	
	gsensors (gnome-sensors)
	
(C)opyright 2003 Vinicius Kursancew

This is an applet to the gnome panel that monitors the system's
sensors.

Features:
 + Refresh rate configurable
 + Warning limits
 + Configurable applet display
 + BEEP!
 + Logging facility
 
To be able to use this applet you will need the following:
 + lm-senors kernel module
 + libsensors installed
 + GNOME2

To build you will need the development packages for:
 + gnome-panel-2
 + libsensors
 + GTK+2.x
 + libgconf-2
 + libpango-1
 + libbobobo-ui-2